    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Steering Wheel button handling -> gets LIN switch details from LIN signals and writes to Rte. Also calculates Dimming interpolation for Cluster HUD."
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Requirement document："
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
